## Files Created

### Database Models
| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [StudentProfile.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/StudentProfile.ts) | Extended student registration data (gender, DOB, mobile, qualification, emailVerified) |
| [EmailOTP.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/EmailOTP.ts) | Hashed OTP with MongoDB TTL auto-expiry, attempt counter, rate-limit timestamp |
| [Resume.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Resume.ts) | Full resume with embedded education, skills, internship, experience, languages |

### Backend APIs
| Route | Method | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| [/api/auth/register](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/register/route.ts) | POST | Creates User + StudentProfile, prevents duplicates |
| [/api/auth/send-otp](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/send-otp/route.ts) | POST | Sends branded OTP email via Hostinger SMTP, 60s rate limit |
| [/api/auth/verify-otp](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/verify-otp/route.ts) | POST | Validates OTP — max 3 attempts, 5-min expiry, bcrypt compare |
| [/api/auth/resend-otp](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/resend-otp/route.ts) | POST | Resend OTP (delegates to send-otp with same rate limiting) |
| [/api/student/resume](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/resume/route.ts) | GET + POST | Fetch or upsert resume data, session-protected |

### Frontend Pages
| Page | Path | Description |
|---|---|---|
| [register/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28public%29/register/page.tsx) | `/register` | 4-step form: Basic → Academic → OTP → Success |
| [resume/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28student%29/student/resume/page.tsx) | `/student/resume` | Guided accordion resume builder with dropdown-heavy, helper-text UI |
| [preview/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28student%29/student/resume/preview/page.tsx) | `/student/resume/preview` | A4 printable resume preview with PDF download via `html2pdf.js` |

### Other Changes
- [student/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28student%29/student/page.tsx) — Added **"Your Career Tools"** quick-action cards to student dashboard
- [.env](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/.env) — Added Hostinger SMTP credentials (`verification@ldmcollege.com`)
- [html2pdf.d.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/types/html2pdf.d.ts) — TypeScript declarations for html2pdf.js

---

## User Flow

```
/register (Step 1: Name, Gender, DOB, Mobile, Email, Password)
    ↓ Continue
(Step 2: Qualification, Year of Passing, English Level)
    ↓ Continue → POST /api/auth/register → POST /api/auth/send-otp
(Step 3: 6-digit OTP boxes, 5-min countdown, resend after 60s)
    ↓ Verify OTP → POST /api/auth/verify-otp
(Step 4: 🎉 "You're registered!" → Login to Dashboard)
    ↓
/login → Student Dashboard
    ↓ Click "Resume Builder"
/student/resume (Career Objective → Skills → Education → Internship → Languages)
    ↓ "Preview My Resume →"
/student/resume/preview (A4 layout, Download PDF button)
```

---

## Security Features Implemented

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| OTP hashing | `bcrypt.hash(otp, 10)` — never stored as plain text |
| Auto-delete expired OTPs | MongoDB TTL index on `expiresAt` |
| Max OTP attempts | 3 attempts — locked after 3rd failure |
| Resend rate limiting | 60-second cooldown enforced server-side |
| Duplicate account prevention | Returns same message regardless (anti-enumeration) |
| Password hashing | `bcrypt.hash(password, 12)` |
| Resume route protection | `getServerSession()` check — students only |

---

## Before Going Live

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Restart `npm run dev`** after adding the SMTP credentials to [.env](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/.env) — Next.js only reads env vars at startup.

> [!NOTE]
> **Attendance by Photo** feature was deferred to a separate phase as planned. The current dashboard shows existing attendance records.
